      "set:html": "<p>The Controller task has priority 2, Blink has priority 1. Why? Because when Controller calls <code dir=\"auto\">vTaskSuspend(hBlink)</code>, it needs to preempt Blink immediately. If both had priority 1, the suspend would only take effect at the next tick — a subtle timing difference.</p>"
